---
title: Asian Sweet Soy Beef Bowl with Honey-Soy Veggies & Sesame Dressing
description: Salt and pepper are always there, ready whenever you need that extra push of seasoning, doing their duty in every dish. Now
it’s their time to shine in this beef and rice bowl. Salt and pepper beef is the standout, but don’t forget those honey soy veggies
because we sure won’t!
